measure.CatchLine: Requires the approval of an urban renewal plan by the electors of a municipality proposing a plan or a substantial amendment to a plan.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: The Act would require that an urban renewal plan or an amendment to a plan be approved by voters. (Flesch Readability Score: 67.3). 
	Requires the approval of an urban renewal plan by the electors of a municipality proposing a plan or a substantial amendment to a plan.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to urban renewal; creating new provisions; and amending ORS 457.085, 457.089, 457.095, 457.105, 457.120, 457.125 and 457.135.
measure.FiscalImpact: May have fiscal impact, but no statement yet issued
measure.RevenueImpact: May have revenue impact, but no statement yet issued

historyActions.ActionText: First reading. Referred to Speaker's desk.
